Class CustomerData

  • java.lang.Object
    • xml.CustomerData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICustomerData

    public class CustomerData
extends java.lang.Object
implements ICustomerData
    Class to hold the CustomerData of the requirement analysis. This class provides JAXB support and can be accessed via the ICustomerData Interface. Getter and Setter must be provided to be JAXB conform. It is implemented in the CustomXMLFormat.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    3852430
    See Also:
    ICustomerData, CustomXMLFormat
